name: Wishbone Earrings
description:
A pair of sterling silver wishbones to decorate your ears. They measure approximately 5.5cm in length and are supplied with clear rubber backs to ensure they stay securely in place. 

All items are made to order so please allow up to 3 weeks for delivery, although if you need something in a hurry message us and we'll see what we can do!

name: Wishbone Necklace
description:
Sterling silver necklace cast from a real wishbone and fastened with a silver safety pin. The necklace is 95cm long and can be worn low slung or doubled up to show off the clasp. 

All items are made to order so please allow up to 3 weeks for delivery, although if you need something in a hurry message us and we'll see what we can do!

name: Wishbone Ring

name: Wishbone Bracelet
description:

All items are made to order so please allow up to 3 weeks for delivery, although if you need something in a hurry message us and we'll see what we can do!

name: Id Necklace or Bracelet
description:
This one looks just as good on guys or girls and it's adjustable to give you a perfect fit. The Id necklace might at first glance look like a traditional ID necklace but jewellery always tells people something about you, make it more interesting than what your name is: show your bones, show your true self. 

A sterling silver necklace featuring a bone measuring approx 50mm on a cable chain fastened with a safety pin clasp. This design is available as a necklace or bracelet. The necklace is adjustable to approx 400, 430 and 460mm (16", 17", 18")  and the bracelet to approx 180, 190 and 200mm (7", 7.5", 8").

All items are made to order so please allow up to 3 weeks for delivery, although if you need something in a hurry message us and we'll see what we can do!

name: 5 Tiny Pieces Set Of Rings
description:
Set of 5 sterling silver rings: heart, horseshoe, circle, triangle and bar.
Buy the whole set and get the equivalent of one ring free! Wear them all together or scattered here and there, if you would like your rings in different sizes to wear on different fingers just send us a message when your order. 


All items are made to order so we can size your ring for a perfect fit, just message us if you know your exact size or if you need a size which isn't listed (we'll do what we can within the confines of the design).  Please allow up to 3 weeks for delivery, although if you need something in a hurry message us and we'll see what we can do!

name: 5 Tiny Pieces Triangle Pendant On Leather Thong
description:
Did you ever find buried treasure when you were little: corroded by it's time underground but beautiful and precious. 

Featuring a sterling silver triangle pendant and bone toggle on a black leather thong.

All items are made to order so please allow up to 3 weeks for delivery, although if you need something in a hurry message us and we'll see what we can do!

name: 5 Tiny Pieces Ear studs
description:
Set of 5 sterling silver ear studs with, wear them all at once (if your piercings allow, we don't recommend adding extra holes yourself just because you can't decide between a heart and a horseshoe) or one at a time. The 5 pieces are: heart, triangle, horseshoe, bar and circle. 

Good news for those of you who like some symmetry in your lives, we've had so many requests for pairs of studs that we've decided to offer these ear studs as either a set of 5 pairs or as single studs so you can get a matching pair (or a non-matching pair) or maybe just the one.

All items are made to order so please allow up to 3 weeks for delivery, although if you need something in a hurry message us and we'll see what we can do!

name: 3 Bone Triangle Pendant On Leather Thong
description:
Made from three delicate sterling silver bones, the Triangle pendant hangs from a simple leather thong with a bone toggle clasp. 

The pendant measures approx 15mm from base to apex.

All items are made to order so please allow up to 3 weeks for delivery, although if you need something in a hurry message us and we'll see what we can do!

name: 4 Bone Bar Necklace
description:
Four delicate sterling silver bones form the focus of this necklace, with a light oxidised finish on the bones and a heavier matt oxidisation on the chain (this will polish off on the edges over time giving a antique look).  

The necklace measures approx 52cm (20") in total. 

All items are made to order so please allow up to 3 weeks for delivery, although if you need something in a hurry message us and we'll see what we can do!

name: Bonesy Jr Ring
description:
Sterling silver skull ring. 
Cast from an original hand carved wax.

All items are made to order so we can size your ring for a perfect fit, just message us if you know your exact size or if you need a size which isn't listed (we'll do what we can within the confines of the design, Bonesy Jr is suited to more slender fingers, relatively speaking, so if you're above a size S you might want to consider Bonesy's Big Bro).  Please allow up to 3 weeks for delivery, although if you need something in a hurry message us and we'll see what we can do!

name: Bonesy Jr's Big Bro
description:
The name says it all, a sterling silver skull ring that's a dead ringer for Bonesy Jr but scaled up. One for the guys (or girls who like to live large). 
Cast from an original hand carved wax. 

All items are made to order so we can size your ring for a perfect fit, just message us if you know your exact size or if you need a size which isn't listed (we'll do what we can within the confines of the design, Big Bro will go up to Z+ but won't work so well in smaller sizes take a look at Bonesy Jr if you have skinny fingers).  Please allow up to 3 weeks for delivery, although if you need something in a hurry message us and we'll see what we can do!

name: Wishbone Twist Earrings
description:
At first glance these earrings could be a kiss or a ribbon.  There's an Victorian feel here, feminine but decidedly dark.  Cast from a real wishbones they give the distinctive form a new twist. 

Cast in sterling silver and formed by hand these earrings measure approximately 5cm (2") in length.

name: Wishbone Twist Ring
description:
Sterling silver crossover ring crafted from a casting of a wishbone. Measures approximately 3cm across the front.


All items are made to order so we can size your ring for a perfect fit, just message us if you know your exact size or if you need a size which isn't listed (we'll do what we can within the confines of the design).  Please allow up to 3 weeks for delivery, although if you need something in a hurry message us and we'll see what we can do!

name: Wishbone Twist Necklace
description:
At first glance this pendant could be a kiss or a ribbon.  There's an Victorian feel here, feminine but decidedly dark.  Cast from a real wishbones it give the distinctive form a new twist. 

Measuring approximately 95cm (37.5") and fastened with a bone toggle clasp this sterling silver necklace can be worn doubled up or long and low.

name: Broken Wishbone Necklaces
description:
"You and I are more than friends.  We're like a really small gang"

... and gangs don't give each other broken heart, friends forever necklaces... but a broken wishbone? Even a Hell's Angel could get away with that.  So keep one half and give the other to someone special (if you want to help them out with a little extra luck give them the bigger half, if you want to get really sentimental and tell them you got all the luck when you found them then keep the bigger half for yourself). Oh, and if you're kind of a loner they look great worn together as a pair.

Two halves of a wishbone cast in sterling silver each on a leather thong fastened with a bone toggle clasp.

name: Long Bone Earrings
description: Simple and elegant these long bar earrings are cast in sterling silver from a pair of bones.  They measure approximately 6.5cm (2.5").
